<h1 align="center">🎟️ PHP Product & Coupon Generation System</h1>

<p align="center">
  <b>A unique mini PHP project that allows users to generate discount coupons for available products, with full admin control.</b>
</p>

<hr/>

<h2>🛠️ Features</h2>

<h3>👤 User Functionality</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Register and login as a user</li>
  <li>View all available products</li>
  <li>Generate one-time discount coupons for products</li>
  <li>View and redeem coupons</li>
</ul>

<h3>🛡️ Admin Functionality</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Pre-registered admin login</li>
  <li>Add, edit, and delete products</li>
  <li>View all generated coupons (availed or pending) with user details</li>
</ul>

---

<h2>📁 Project Structure</h2>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>File</th>
      <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>login.php</code></td><td>User/Admin login</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>register.php</code></td><td>User registration</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>logout.php</code></td><td>Logout functionality</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>admin_dashboard.php</code></td><td>Admin dashboard</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>user_dashboard.php</code></td><td>User dashboard</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>add_product.php</code></td><td>Admin adds products</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>edit_product.php</code></td><td>Admin edits products</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>delete_product.php</code></td><td>Admin deletes products</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>generate_coupon.php</code></td><td>Users generate coupons</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>redeem_coupon.php</code></td><td>Users redeem coupons</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>view_coupon.php</code></td><td>Admin views all coupons</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>my_coupon.php</code></td><td>Users view their coupons</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>db.php</code></td><td>Database connection</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

---

<h2>🚀 How to Use</h2>

<h3>🔑 Admin</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Login using the default admin credentials.</li>
  <li>Add products with name, price (USD), and discount (1–100%).</li>
  <li>View, edit, or delete products via dashboard table.</li>
  <li>Monitor all user-generated coupons and redemption status.</li>
</ol>

<h3>👥 User</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Register with email & password.</li>
  <li>Login to access your user dashboard.</li>
  <li>View all products and generate one coupon per product.</li>
  <li>Once generated, the coupon button is disabled for that product.</li>
  <li>Redeem coupons anytime and get a confirmation alert.</li>
</ol>

